(RFP 2026: Nordic Utilities Hybrid Cloud Modernization Program) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Document Type: Requirement Specification / Tender) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. BACKGROUND AND OBJECTIVE) Tj
T* (---------------------------) Tj
T* (Nordic Utilities intends to modernize its customer billing, outage management, and analytics) Tj
T* (workloads into a hybrid cloud operating model during 2026-2028.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The selected vendor must deliver an Azure-centric target architecture while retaining selected) Tj
T* (on-premise systems for regulatory and latency-sensitive operations.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The customer expects a phased migration with zero unplanned downtime for customer billing and) Tj
T* (critical grid operations.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2. SCOPE OF WORK) Tj
T* (----------------) Tj
T* (Design, implement, and operate a hybrid landing zone including network segmentation, identity) Tj
T* (federation, backup strategy, and disaster recovery runbooks.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Migrate 140 applications in three waves. Wave 1 shall include shared services, Wave 2 shall) Tj
T* (include customer-facing workloads, and Wave 3 shall include analytics and archive systems.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The bidder must provide a 24/7 managed services model for platform operations, incident handling,) Tj
T* (patching, and monthly performance reporting.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (3. MANDATORY TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS) Tj
T* (-----------------------------------) Tj
T* (The platform must support multi-region failover with an RTO of 60 minutes and an RPO of 15 minutes) Tj
T* (for Tier-1 systems.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (All production workloads shall use customer-managed keys for encryption at rest.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Identity management must integrate with existing Entra ID tenant and enforce conditional access.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The vendor shall implement Infrastructure as Code using Terraform, with all modules provided to) Tj
T* (the customer repository.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Monitoring must include log analytics, distributed tracing, and proactive alerting with escalation) Tj
T* (paths.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (All environments must pass CIS benchmark hardening profiles and monthly vulnerability remediation) Tj
T* (SLAs.) Tj
T* () Tj
ET
